{"title":"宣誓（二首）","authors":["戈壁舟"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣誓（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们举起手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要叫高山排队走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们举起手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要叫大河倒着流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们举起手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要去参加大战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向田地要粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向高山要油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向柴火要棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向野草要酒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个天大的决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要听党的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有甚么不能够！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"5月2日返蓉之夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着计划下去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跟春风春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着计划下去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把锄头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件行李；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有满腔热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚强毅力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要在金色的秋天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带回胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"5月14日成都"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}